Package: rppr
Title: Rural Postman Problem Solver
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Matthew Lincoln",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mlincoln@andrew.cmu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4387-3384"))
Description: Implements a solution to the rural postman problem,
    finding efficient paths through a network that visit a specified
    subset of edges.
